 powder and mix <b>20 sec\/90°C\/speed 2<b>."},{"content":"Add tomatoes and blend <b>20 sec\/speed 5<b>, until smooth."},{"content":"Add lamb and cook <b>40-60 min\/100°C\/\/speed 1<b> or until meat is tender."},{"content":"Add salt, pepper and reserved spinach paste and cook <b>2 min\/90°C\/\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Add lime juice and gently stir with aid of spatula. Transfer into a serving bowl. Top with yoghurt before serving."}],"hintsAndTricks":["To make your own ghee, garlic paste, ginger paste and garam masala, please refer to the recipes on this recipe chip.","Serve with your favourite bread or rice. We served ours with Garlic and coriander naan (please refer to the recipe on this recipe chip)."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 30m","6 portions"]}